      "text": "ar mannu Balsi/ es luhdsu to\nKUNGSu ar mannu Balsi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es iṣgahschu mannu\nSchehlochann preekſch winna/\nes iṣtahstu winna Breekſchá\nmannas Behdas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Rad manna Sirḍs apival-\ndsinata irr/ tad tu finni preekſch\nman Zeltu/ tee leek man Wal-\ngits us to Zeltu/ kur es eemu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es skattohs pa labbo Roh-\nku/ un redsi/ tur newaid ne wee-\nna/ kas mannu grib pasiht/ es ne\nwarn ne kur isbehgt/ ne weens\ngabda par mannu Dwehseli.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tewis peefauzu es KUNgs/\nes tafku : Tu efi mannaZerriba/\nmanna Dalliba eekſch tahs Sem-\nmes to Dsihwo.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Nemin wehrá mannu\nKleegschann/ jo es ejmu tohti no-\nnihzis/ iṣglahb mannu no man-\nneem Wajatajeem/ jo tee irr\nman wiffai warreni.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Iswedd mannu Dwehteli\nno Zeetuma/ ka es tawam Wahr-\nDain pateizu/ tee Taifnee ap-\nfahrt mannu mettifees/ kad tu\nman labba darrifi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "manahu Luhgschanu/ a\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ne eij Sohdá ar tam\nKalpu/ jo tawá Preekschá ne i\nne kahds Dsihws taiſns.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo tas Eenaidneeks wa\nmannu Dwehteli/ wiṣch\nminn mannu Dsihwibu\nSemmes/ wiṣch leek man\nTumfiba/ ka tohs/ kas jaw fer\nnomirrufschi irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un mans Gars eekſch ma\nnim noginst/ manna Sirḍs eekſ\nmannis irr nonihkufi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Es peeminnu tohs zittkah\ntigns Laikus/ es dohmaju no w\nfeem taweein Darbeem/ es ru\nnaju pee jewis no tawu Roh\nDarrischanahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Es tspattu faivas R\nkas prett tewi/ manna Dweh\nle irr tawá Preekscha/ ka wee\niskaltusi Semme/ Sela.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Paklauti mann dr\nKUNGS/ mans Gars suhdah\nne apflep tawn Watgu preek\nmannim/ ka es ne tohpu li\nka tee/ kas Dsitkuná nogrim\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Leez mann agri dsird\ntawu Schehlastibu/ jo es pal\nschohs us tewi/ darri man fin\nmu to Zeltu/ us ko man ja-e\njo us tewi neffahs man\nDwehsele.\n"
    }
  ],
